    "• RQ3: What are the primary challenges for the current state-of-the-art in LLM-based unit test generation, and what opportunities do they present for future research?By answering these questions, this survey provides not only a structured overview of the current landscape but also a clear roadmap.",
    "This roadmap, informed by systems engineering principles, is intended to guide the transition of LLM-based testing from academic exploration to robust industrial practice.To present our analysis systematically, the subsequent sections of this paper are organized as follows.",
    "Section 2 lays the foundation for our argument.",
    "By reviewing the classic principles of automated unit test generation, we precisely define the \"semantic gap\" that traditional methods struggle to overcome and clarify why large language models are seen as a pivotal technology for addressing it.",
    "Section 3 details the methodology of our systematic literature review."
